description: Number of 5-card poker hands with deuces wild of 5-of-a-kind, royal flush, straight flush, 4-of-a-kind, full house, flush, straight, 3-of-a-kind, two pairs, one pair, no pair.
references: "The Complete Guide To Winning Poker", Albert Morehead, chap 8.
example: There are 672 ways to get five-of-a-kind with deuces wild.
author: _Jud McCranie_, Oct 21 2000
